>\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e701b680d76cf5e0157903aa9f31240dc6ae64d3","tid":1360698,"uid":236847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:44:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88837deba5031b4997fd9a5d3ae8bd30d1adeeb9","tid":1360698,"uid":198223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:20:44.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"a9cfca7874b262f40401954c0b2c95992d2550c5","tid":1360698,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:22:12.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}